William Fox, Respondent, v. Jacob W. Loeb, Appellant. (Appeal No. 1.)

Order denying motion to vacate notice of examination before trial affirmed, with ten dollars costs and disbursements; examination to proceed on five days’ notice at the place and hour stated in the order. No opinion. Lazansky, P. J., Young, Kapper, Carswell and Davis, JJ., concur.
